"title": "5459: prince",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5459",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The son of a king, or a very important official, leader or ruler. The title is given to Jesus Christ and also to angelic spirits (in particular Michael and Satan).</p>\n<h2>A prince as the son of a king</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:22\">2CH 11:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:32\">2SA 13:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:6-2Kgs10:8\">2KI 10:6–10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:2\">2KI 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:16\">PSA 45:16</a></p>\n<h2>A prince as someone occupying a very important position</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:26\">GEN 49:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:16\">DEU 33:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:6\">GEN 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1SA 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:38\">2SA 3:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:8\">PSA 113:8</a></p>\n<h2>A prince as a very important official, leader or ruler</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:3\">EST 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:18\">NUM 21:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:8\">NUM 22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:13-Num22:15\">NUM 22:13–22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh13:21\">JOS 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:15\">JDG 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:4\">2CH 21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:8\">2CH 22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:8\">EZR 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:9\">EST 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:27\">PSA 68:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:16\">PRO 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:12\">EZK 21:12</a>EZK <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:6\">22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:8-Ezek45:9\">EZK 45:8–45:9</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:2-Ezek38:3\">EZK 38:2–38:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:6\">DAN 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:4\">HOS 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>The Messiah is described as a prince</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">ISA 9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:24\">EZK 34:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:25\">EZK 37:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:3\">EZK 44:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:11\">DAN 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:25\">DAN 8:25</a></p>\n<h2>Angelic spirits (whether good or evil) are described as princes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:13\">DAN 10:13</a></strong> <em>The prince of the Persian kingdom was possibly a demon, exercising influence in the interests of Satan.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:20-Dan10:21\">DAN 10:20–10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:1\">DAN 12:1</a></p>\n<h2>Satan is described as a prince</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:34\">MAT 9:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:24\">MAT 12:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:22\">MRK 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:15\">LUK 11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:30\">JHN 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:11\">JHN 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">EPH 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>The splendour of the princess</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:13\">PSA 45:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a></p>",
